Bakeri, GH. and Rahimnejad, M. 2013.  KINETICS STUDY OF HYDRAZODICARBONAMIDE SYNTHESIS REACTION. Chemical Industry &amp; Chemical Engineering Quarterly, vol 2, 19, pp 273−279
</comment>
